<title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="lec-VVVVVV" text="title"/></title>

<statement>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <sidebyside>
        <p>¿Qué fracción del rectángulo está sombreada? Explica cómo lo sabes.</p>
        <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151728">
          <shortdescription>Diagram. Rectangle partitioned into 8 equal parts, 5 parts shaded.</shortdescription>
        </image>
      </sidebyside>
    </li>
    <li>
      <sidebyside>
        <p>Colorea <m>\frac{4}{6}</m> del rectángulo.</p>
        <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151729">
          <shortdescription>Diagram. Rectangle.</shortdescription>
        </image>
      </sidebyside>
    </li>
  </ol>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++++++++++]</p>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <p><m>\frac{5}{8}</m> . Sample response: There are 8 equal parts and 5 of them are shaded.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>Sample response:</p>
      <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-152487">
        <shortdescription>Diagram.</shortdescription>
      </image>
    </li>
  </ol>
</solution>

</exercise>
